<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v17" title="Q19_v17" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>El costo de un objeto se modela como 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      unidades monetarias. Al comprar 2 objetos idénticos, un estudiante representa el costo total como 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>. ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones simplificadas representa el costo total de los 2 objetos?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>21</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El costo total se obtiene multiplicando 2 por 3√7, lo que da 6√7. Esta opción es 2√21, y no coincide con 6√7 porque, por ejemplo, al cuadrar ambas expresiones se obtiene 84 para 2√21 y 252 para 6√7.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>7</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al simplificar 2·3√7, primero se multiplican los coeficientes: 2·3 = 6, y la raíz √7 se mantiene. Por eso el costo total es 6√7.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>14</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El costo total es 2·3√7 = 6√7. Esta opción es 3√14, y no representa el mismo valor. Al cuadrar ambas expresiones se obtiene 126 para 3√14 y 252 para 6√7, por lo tanto son distintas.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>49</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Como √49 = 7, esta opción equivale a 6·7 = 42. En cambio, el costo total simplificado es 6√7, que no es igual a 42.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la expresión que representa el costo total</strong></p>
            <p>Si un objeto cuesta</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>entonces 2 objetos idénticos cuestan</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Multiplicar los factores numéricos</strong></p>
            <p>En la expresión anterior, los números fuera de la raíz son 2 y 3. Entonces:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>La raíz</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:msqrt>
                <m:mn>7</m:mn>
              </m:msqrt>
            </m:math>
            <p>se mantiene igual, porque no se está multiplicando por otra raíz.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Escribir la expresión simplificada</strong></p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la que muestra</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>que corresponde a la <strong>opción B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El costo total simplificado de los 2 objetos es</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>6</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>7</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>por lo tanto la respuesta correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>